Title

Cards Validation for Release 5.0

Description

Perform validation of all cards included in Release 5.0 to ensure each feature, fix, enhancement, or configuration update works as expected. This includes verifying functional behavior, UI changes, backend updates, integrations, and any associated workflows.

Acceptance Criteria

Given all cards for Release 5.0 are deployed,
When validation is executed for each card,
Then all functionalities should work as expected with no errors or regressions across impacted areas.

Title

Smoke Test Post Card Merge to Master in Dev Environment

Description

Perform a smoke test in the Dev environment after merging the latest cards into the master branch. The objective is to ensure that the merged changes do not introduce any breakages, and core functionalities continue to work as expected.

Acceptance Criteria

Given the latest cards are merged into the master branch in the Dev environment,
When a smoke test is performed,
Then all major functionalities should work without errors or regression issues.
